EFI.name: Contains everything required to generate the configuration source code

dictionary.name: TransmissionRatio
dictionary.desc: Converts gear to a ratio used to calculate MPH

dictionary.name: EncoderRatio
dictionary.desc: Ratio to crankshaft rpm, 2 for cam driven, 1 for crank driven.

dictionary.name: EncoderCompare
dictionary.desc: Index of the historical pulse to compare

dictionary.name: EncoderSyncHigh
dictionary.desc: Whether to look at low or high pulse values

dictionary.name: EncoderSyncShort
dictionary.desc: Sync on the shortest or longest pulse

dictionary.name: EncoderCountOffset
dictionary.desc: Offset edges to add to the sync edge

dictionary.name: EncoderDegreesOffset
dictionary.desc: Offset degrees to add the final sync edge

dictionary.name: AxleRatio
dictionary.desc: Rear axle ratio to calculate speed from rpm

dictionary.name: TireDiameter
dictionary.desc: Tire diameter to calculate speed from rpm

dictionary.name: GallonWeight
dictionary.desc: The weight of a gallon of gas to calculate mpg

dictionary.name: CrankingRPM
dictionary.desc: RPM below this is not considered running

dictionary.name: MaxRPM
dictionary.desc: Maximum rpm engine should ever turn

dictionary.name: WOT
dictionary.desc: Throttle percent where a switch to the wide open tables is used
